Residual risk:
- The manual scoped-selection UI itself is only covered through the pure scope-filter helpers, not a full Shift-Tab interactive end-to-end path. That is deliberate for now because the scheduled/keymap dance is much more brittle than the underlying scope semantics, which are now tested directly.
